short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Paper.io 2 is a real-time multiplayer game where you have to capture as much territory as possible and become a king of the map.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,et,fa,fi,f:
PAPER.IO 2 UNBLOKED game is available in the chrome web store just install it and play PAPER.IO 2 UNBLOKED game.

Extend your area as much as possible. Use your paper block to steal the area from your online opponents in this online web game. Capture as much space as possible and try to get the highest score in the lobby. If you move outside your own color, your tail becomes exposed. You will be eliminated when someone manages to catch your tail. So you need to take risks to expand your colored area.


how to play :- Move - Mouse/Arrow-keys

thank you-:)
